@pp_minority
title: <span style="color: var(--pp); font-style: italic;">PP</span> Minority Government
subtitle: PP governs alone, tolerated from the outside. [? if congreso_coalition_pp_min_talks: Held up by tolerations they'll have to bargain for. ?]
view-if: congreso_coalition_pp_min_s > congreso_s_majority - 50
choose-if: congreso_coalition_pp_min_reach
unavailable-subtitle: Even with outside support, PP alone can't clear investiture.
on-arrival: {!
    // TODO — form a PP single-party (minority) cabinet, externally supported.
    //   • president = pp; Cs + the right-leaning minors sit OUTSIDE (support/abstain).
!}

